                <label>[B]$INFO[Window(10000).Property(EPG.Title)][COLOR=C0C0C0C0] â€¢ [/COLOR][COLOR=FFFFFFFF]$INFO[Window(10000).Property(EPG.SEtitle)][/COLOR][/B]</label>
            </control>
        </control>
